sub_title: Founder and Chief Marketing Officer at Digerati
summary:
Serial entrepreneur, growth-hacking enthusiast, "employee first" believer, business scaler, and servant leader with 15 years of leadership experience in people management & performance management building successful cultures and thought leaders.

Deep domain expertise in digital marketing, lead generation, and conversion optimization.

Leadership Highlights
- Strong command of business and management principles as they pertain to development, resource allocation, process building, and leading others. 
- Inspirational team player with excellent public speaking ability and interpersonal communication.
- Initiator and problem-solver using creativity, technology, data, automation, and assets to break down and overcome organizational obstacles. 
- Lifelong learner committed to staying on top of the best current and emerging business practices and changing technologies.
